\"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"a stepping stone\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His 'potcova' journey began during the Rio 2016 Olympics, specifically during the 100m final featuring Usain Bolt.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9995952223044207, \"rank\": 0.0004049403091986142, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.812399363549976e-17, \"text\": \"2016 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2464, \"end\": 2474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His 'potcova' journey\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spence, armed with his pot covers, travelled to Half-Way-Tree Square and, along with hundreds of others, prepared to celebrate Bolt's victory - and celebrate they did.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spence\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"his pot covers\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"Half-Way-Tree Square\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2544}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"Bolt's victory\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quite obliviously, he was captured on video during the celebration, which got posted, went viral, and the rest is history.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"video\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the celebration\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, he was interviewed on mainstream media during the festivities and, inspired by the \\\"Big Deal\\\", the name of a meal recently launched at that time by a popular fast-food chain, he coined the phrase, \\\"Jamaica a di big deal and everything else a small fries and side order!\\\"\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.472094796976019e-23, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mainstream media\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2820}, {\"ngram\": \"the festivities\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Big Deal\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"a meal\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"a popular fast-food chain\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2955}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"a small fries\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"side order\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This laid dormant until 2020 when it was reposted on someone's social media page and the phrase grew wings.\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This laid dormant\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"someone's social media page\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"wings\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another popular social media influencer reintroduced the phrase in 2022, during the 60th anniversary of Jamaica's Independence, and its popularity grew exponentially.\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3265, \"end\": 3272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.472094796976019e-23, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another popular social media influencer\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"the 60th anniversary\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"its popularity\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, Spence has never received the warranted recognition as the creator of the phrase and has not found a suitable channel to monetise its usage.\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spence\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"the warranted recognition\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"the creator\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"a suitable channel\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"its usage\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in the years since, a number of highly successful companies have used his image in promotional activities and advertisements without him gaining any financial benefit.\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ye